{"tid":1318374,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【新抗爭哲學】和理非+勇武=智仁勇","createTime":"2019-07-15T02:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T02:30:43.000Z","uid":125508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8f60057e4baeb86bda0baf3839a609e9b12846ca","tid":1318374,"uid":125508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:30:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">智仁勇</span></span>是孔子的三達德：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">智，知者不惑</span></span>：道德判別的智慧，將信仰和哲理推進政治；不為紅媒迷亂，永遠記住道理在我方。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">仁，仁者不憂</span></span>：建基在智慧上的仁愛，不做鄉願，貫徹大德。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">勇，勇者不懼</span></span>：建基在仁愛上的勇敢，內心存對香港的愛，對外勇敢發聲，勇武抗爭。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>和理非和勇武只是手段，只要掌握智仁勇三德，和理非也能勇武，為母則強；勇武也能和理非，以柔制剛。</strong></span></span>"}]}